# User Login, Sound Playback & Utilities

A simple Python application for user login, audio playback, and basic utilities like a calculator and personal notes.

## Features

- User registration and login using local text files
- Password validation and management
- View user ID and play associated sound
- Simple calculator functionality
- Daily note system
- Sound playback with unit and tens decomposition for IDs

## Installation

1. Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/your-repo.git
cd your-repo


